    <string name="about_app_description">📝 PromptLog - Personal Offline Application\n\nPromptLog is a personal and offline application created to record and consult prompts used by users in interactions with AI language models (such as ChatGPT, Claude, etc.).\n\n🎯 Main Objective:\nAllow users to save their most useful prompts and respective responses, even when away from the computer and without internet access.\n\n✨ Features:\n• Registration of custom prompts\n• Complete offline storage\n• Categorization by themes\n• Priority system\n• Favorite marking\n• Organization with tags\n• Intuitive and friendly interface\n• Quick access to saved prompts\n\nVersion: 1.0.0\nDeveloped as an academic project for the Android Frameworks course</string>
